					It has been observed from our attendance record that you have remained absent from <b> #Last_Attended_Date# </b> without any prior intimation or leave application. 
				<p>
				<p style="text-align:justify">
					Absenting yourself from duties without prior intimation is a mis-conduct for which necessary actions can be initiated on you.
				<p>
				<p style="text-align:justify">
